name: Silent Sobs 03
description:
Primal screams,

Reverberating off the edges of our consciousness,

Begging us to listen.

It is the call of the hurting.

It can be too loud, too painful, to make a sound.


Once we finally learn to hear it,

Do we join in to the crescendo and add to the cry for help?

Or do we stop to listen and scramble to figure out how to heal it?
